Parse attribute modifications from string to dictionary.

Parameters

  • s (str) ‚Äì required, string of attribute modifications in format ‚Äò<feature type>:<standard attribute field name>=<nonstandard attribute field name>,<standard attribute field name>=<nonstandard attribute field name>;<feature type>:<standard attribute field name>=<nonstandard attribute field name>‚Äô (e.g. ‚ÄòmRNA:Parent=Locus_id‚Äô)

  • attr_sep (str) ‚Äì delimiter for attribute modifications of same feature type (default=‚Äô,‚Äô)

  • feature_sep (str) ‚Äì delimiter for feature types (default=‚Äô;‚Äô)

  • fa_sep (str) ‚Äì delimiter between feature type and attribute modifications (default=‚Äô:‚Äô)

  • alias_sep (str) ‚Äì delimiter between standard attribute field name and non-standard attribute field name (default=‚Äô=‚Äô)

Returns

parsed attribute modifications in format

{<feature>: {<standard attribute field name>: <nonstandard attribute field name>}}
